<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.8.9">
<l>veṇṇiṟat tōytayir taṉṉai veḷvaraip piṉmuṉe ḻuntu</l>
<l>kaṇṇuṟaṅ kātē yiruntu kaṭaiyavun tāṉvallaḷ kolō</l>
<l>voṇṇiṟat tāmaraic ceṅka ṇulakaḷan tāṉeṉ makaḷai</l>
<l>paṇṇaṟai yāppaṇi koṇṭu paricaṟa vāṇṭiṭuṅ kolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will she, rising before dawn,</l>
<l rend="indent">[her] eyes being without sleep,</l>
<l>be able to churn the curds</l>
<l rend="indent">so that they curdle into a white colour?</l>
<l>Will he who measured the world,</l>
<l rend="indent">[his] red eyes [like] the bright coloured lotus,</l>
<l>take [her] in service in a manner that is without dharma</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] rule her without dignity?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
